---
title: Pan-Fried Gnocchi & Creamy Mushrooms with Zingy Rocket & Parmesan
description: Pillowy gnocchi meets a luscious mushroom sauce in this cosy, flavour-packed dish. Bright balsamic glazed rocket and a sprinkle of Parmesan—comfort food with a twist!
